            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a href="https://duepublico.uni-duisburg-essen.de" class="btn btn-primary">To the 'old' DuEPublico ...</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mt-3">
      <h3 class="card-header">
        Open Access E-Publications
      </h3>
      <div class="card-body">
        <img src="../images/openaccess.png" alt="Open Access Logo" style="float:left; margin-right:1ex;" />
        <p>
          University members may publish their works online.
          Your primary or secondary publications will be made citeable by assigning an Digital Object Identifier (DOI),
          recording them at the German National Library
          and making the available world-wide in the sense of Open Access.
        </p>
        <p>
          Here on DuEPublico 2 you can already find
          <a
            href="../servlets/solr/select?q=objectType%3Amods+AND+state%3Apublished+AND+category%3A%22collection%3APub%22&amp;fl=*&amp;sort=mods.dateIssued+desc&amp;rows=20">selected Open Access publications</a>.
          We are currently moving all contens from the old to the new system.
          To
          <a href="https://duepublico.uni-duisburg-essen.de/authoring/openaccess.xml">publish new works</a>,
          please fo now still use the old server.
          There you will also find
          <a href="https://duepublico.uni-duisburg-essen.de/authoring/openaccess.xml">all works that have been published so far</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <a href="https://duepublico.uni-duisburg-essen.de/authoring/openaccess.xml" class="btn btn-primary">Open Access publishing via
          DuEPublico ...</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

